Adults of the 
<taxonomicName box="[431,558,615,640]" class="Insecta" family="Dixidae" genus="Dixa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="249" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ubiquita">
